window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>THE PRINCE: Spoiled, reckless, heedless of any wants or needs but his own, sentenced to a terrible fate for his sins against man, woman, and God. </p><p>THE STALLION: Equally spoiled, equally reckless, and bound until death to a bitter servitude. </p><p>THE TURK'S HEIR: Fiercest of rivals, most devoted of enemies, whose armor hides a secret. </p><p>Come into the world of the Arabian Nights, where magic and mystery meet; where justice lays a sinner low, and the magic of the heart turns hate to love. </p>"; 
